data.description: Welcome to this elegant two-story house that offers both comfort and style, with a thoughtfully designed layout to accommodate the needs of a modern family. The kitchen features ample counter space and a convenient island for both cooking and casual dining. One of the highlights of this home is the private primary bedroom suite located on the ground floor. The attached bathroom is a luxurious retreat with double sinks, a walk-in shower, providing a spa-like experience. As you ascend the staircase to the second floor, you'll discover three additional bedrooms with walk-in closets, each with its own charm. Storage will not be an issue for sure. Entertainment is taken to the next level with the inclusion of a dedicated game room and media room on the second floor. Whether it's family game nights or entertaining friends, this space offers versatility and fun for everyone. If this description has piqued your interest, don't wait to set up a showing. Your dream home awaits!
